cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper discusses various generative models such as VAE, GAN, AAE, and ALI(BiGAN) and their relationship with variational inference. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) which covers topics related to generative models and variational inference. Additionally, the paper also discusses computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) applications of these models. The regularization term proposed in the paper also relates to control systems (cs.SY) and neural networks (cs.NE).
